590
00:34:24,030 --> 00:34:25,010
That's right, I don't.

591
00:34:28,390 --> 00:34:30,450
That man has a stable streak of madness.

592
00:34:30,760 --> 00:34:32,740
If he gets upset, he might kill you.

593
00:34:34,030 --> 00:34:35,340
I'm not about to push my friend

594
00:34:35,360 --> 00:34:36,410
into a fire pit.

595
00:34:38,160 --> 00:34:39,450
So you're worried about me?

596
00:34:40,950 --> 00:34:41,820
I thought...

597
00:34:45,360 --> 00:34:45,970
Never mind.

598
00:35:06,320 --> 00:35:07,660
Had your serpent heart taken?

599
00:35:10,880 --> 00:35:12,220
Who's going to stand up for you?

600
00:35:16,640 --> 00:35:18,010
The night of the new moon is coming.

601
00:35:19,950 --> 00:35:21,370
The day we leave the mountain

602
00:35:22,110 --> 00:35:22,970
