657
00:39:00,200 --> 00:39:01,780
So you're finally making your move.

658
00:39:04,680 --> 00:39:05,620
Relax, okay?

659
00:39:13,280 --> 00:39:13,930
Boss.

660
00:39:14,950 --> 00:39:15,780
See how

661
00:39:15,800 --> 00:39:17,530
I'm serving you with such sincerity?

662
00:39:18,390 --> 00:39:19,180
I'm only

663
00:39:19,880 --> 00:39:21,370
going to discuss

664
00:39:21,880 --> 00:39:22,930
about my benefits.

665
00:39:22,950 --> 00:39:24,490
