666
00:39:27,680 --> 00:39:28,530
What benefits?

667
00:39:30,910 --> 00:39:32,180
It's about my blood again?

668
00:39:33,510 --> 00:39:34,050
That's right.

669
00:39:35,990 --> 00:39:36,740
Also,

